  <author>Gravel God Training</author>
  <name>Endurance - Structured Fartlek - 3 - 60min - RPE6-7</name>
  <description>Structured Fartlek — level 3

WARM-UP:
-10min ramp 50%-&gt;65% FTP (RPE 2-3)

MAIN SET:
-2:43 @ 61%-71% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 90-100rpm)
-1min @ 97%-103% FTP (Z4, RPE 6-7, 90-100rpm)
-2:43 @ 61%-71% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 90-100rpm)
