-1min @ 97%-103% FTP (Z4, RPE 6-7, 90-100rpm)
-2:43 @ 61%-71% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 90-100rpm)
-1min @ 97%-103% FTP (Z4, RPE 6-7, 90-100rpm)
-2:43 @ 61%-71% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 90-100rpm)

COOL-DOWN:
-10min spin-down 70%-&gt;50% FTP (RPE 2-3)

HOW TO RIDE IT:
-Steady and comfortable — hold the power, relax the upper body.

DIMENSIONS:
-zones Z2-Z4 · normal cadence · seated · rolling · attack/recover surges

FUEL:
-40-60g carbs/hr.</description>
